<h3 data-section-id="xnb2c2" data-start="515" data-end="533">Immediate Goal</h3>
<p data-start="535" data-end="568">Build <strong data-start="541" data-end="562">Dollar Circle MVP</strong> with:</p>
<p data-start="570" data-end="757">✅ User Registration<br data-start="589" data-end="592">
✅ Login<br data-start="599" data-end="602">
✅ Profile Management<br data-start="622" data-end="625">
✅ Request Help Form<br data-start="644" data-end="647">
✅ Upload Documents<br data-start="665" data-end="668">
✅ Admin Approval Dashboard<br data-start="694" data-end="697">
✅ Contribution Tracking<br data-start="720" data-end="723">
✅ Notifications<br data-start="738" data-end="741">
✅ Wallet History</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1qrtdti" data-start="759" data-end="790">Important Business Decision</h3>
<p data-start="792" data-end="815">Your original idea was:</p>
<blockquote data-start="817" data-end="882">
<p data-start="819" data-end="882">2,000 people automatically send $1 through Zelle to one person.</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="884" data-end="1029">That cannot be implemented directly through Zelle because Zelle does not provide a public API for third-party applications to initiate transfers.</p>
<p data-start="1031" data-end="1060">A more practical approach is:</p>
<ol data-start="1062" data-end="1357">
<li data-section-id="1ix4lum" data-start="1062" data-end="1090">
<p data-start="1065" data-end="1090">Users join Dollar Circle.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2vnwjz" data-start="1091" data-end="1124">
<p data-start="1094" data-end="1124">Users authorize participation.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kayi6x" data-start="1125" data-end="1163">
<p data-start="1128" data-end="1163">Requests are reviewed and approved.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1aw12te" data-start="1164" data-end="1259">
<p data-start="1167" data-end="1259">Contributions are collected through a payment provider that supports developer integrations.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rpmygd" data-start="1260" data-end="1311">
<p data-start="1263" data-end="1311">Funds are distributed to the approved recipient.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1h57py6" data-start="1312" data-end="1357">
<p data-start="1315" data-end="1357">Every transaction is logged and auditable.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 data-section-id="9tpe3h" data-start="1359" data-end="1388">What I can help with next</h3>
<p data-start="1390" data-end="1401">Choose one:</p>
<p data-start="1403" data-end="1647"><strong data-start="1403" data-end="1409">A.</strong> Create the complete database schema<br data-start="1445" data-end="1448">
<strong data-start="1448" data-end="1454">B.</strong> Create the Flutter mobile app structure<br data-start="1494" data-end="1497">
<strong data-start="1497" data-end="1503">C.</strong> Create the backend API architecture<br data-start="1539" data-end="1542">
<strong data-start="1542" data-end="1548">D.</strong> Create the admin dashboard design<br data-start="1582" data-end="1585">
<strong data-start="1585" data-end="1591">E.</strong> Create the nonprofit business plan and investor package</p>
<p data-start="1649" data-end="1737" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">I recommend starting with <strong data-start="1675" data-end="1698">A (database schema)</strong> because everything else depends on it.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c728a27e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c728a27e.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></us