words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="58">To upload the <code data-start="14" data-end="26">schema.sql</code> file to your GitHub repository:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1l1sxxp" data-start="60" data-end="98">Option 1: GitHub Website (Easiest)</h3>
<ol data-start="100" data-end="443">
<li data-section-id="eg840g" data-start="100" data-end="169">
<p data-start="103" data-end="169">Open your repository:<br>
<strong data-start="128" data-end="169"><span class="" data-state="closed"><a target="_blank" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer" rel="noopener">Dollar-Circle Repository<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none select-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75] select-none"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c728a27e.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></span></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="18okihg" data-start="171" data-end="215">
<p data-start="174" data-end="215">Click <strong data-start="180" data-end="194">"Add file"</strong> → <strong data-start="197" data-end="215">"Upload files"</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9x9928" data-start="217" data-end="272">
<p data-start="220" data-end="242">Create a folder named:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="246" data-end="272"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c728a27e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>database</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cwqnen" data-start="274" data-end="325">
<p data-start="277" data-end="293">Upload the file:</p>
