ean, text-light printable match tracker for the World Cup knockout rounds with blank spaces for teams and scores.\"},{\"body\":\"Explain the Summerween trend and give me a low-scare guide to slasher movie terms, without spoilers.\",\"title\":\"Decode Summerween movies\"},{\"title\":\"Compare grocery unit prices\",\"body\":\"Teach me how to compare grocery unit prices when labels use ounces, pounds, sheets, or counts. Give a quick practice example.\"},{\"title\":\"Learn Wimbledon scoring\",\"body\":\"Teach me Wimbledon scoring in plain English, including sets, tiebreaks, and the terms I’ll hear most while watching.\"},{\"title\":\"Create a match-day snack board\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light image of a soccer watch-party snack board with blank labels. Ask my snack style first and avoid logos.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me plan a low-key potluck with a playful theme, easy food categories, and a simple host timeline. Ask me the date and guest count first.\",\"title\":\"Plan a low-key potluck\"},{\"title\":\"Practice interview answers\",\"body\":\"Run a short interview practice for a role I’m applying to. Ask me for the job title, then give one question and feedback at a time.\"},{\"title\":\"Make a day-trip map card\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light visual day-trip card with a route shape, stops, and timing blocks. Ask me for my starting city and trip vibe first.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me choose a few Tour de France stages to watch this year based on drama, scenery, sprint finishes, and mountain days.\",\"title\":\"Choose Tour de France stages\"},{\"title\":\"Compare slides and flip-flops\",\"body\":\"Explain why flip-flops and slides trend every summer, then compare comfort, styling, and when each one makes sense.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a clean, text-light tennis scorecard image with blank rows for sets and tiny court icons.\",\"title\":\"Create a tennis scorecard\"},{\"title\":\"Make a day-out mood board\",\"body\":\"Create an image of a text-light mood board for a playful day